highlights.text: “Exit Sign” by HIEUTHUHAI and marzuz has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 212 days straight.
“Yêu Một Người Có Lẽ” by Lê Nhật Minh is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #85.
Dangrangto has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “một bài hát không vui mấy - Extended Version” is the highest at #26.
“F L Y” by Spectrum is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 25 spots at #70.
